'Yan Majalisar Wales sun damu da cewa za a yi musu kallon mariya
Wasu 'yan majalisa na ƙasar Wales sun yi takaici da shawarar da aka bayar na maye gurbin sunansu da MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan shawara ta samo asali ne daga wani shiri na sauya sunan majalisa, wanda zai zama majalisar kasar Wales.
A fagen siyasa, wasu 'yan majalisa sun ce za a yi wa wannan abin dariya.
Wani dan majalisa na Labor ya nuna cewa rukuninsa na da damuwa game da cewa  yana yin waƙa da Twp da Pwp .
Ga masu karatu da ba su fito daga Wales ba: a harshen Welsh, twp na nufin wawa, kuma pwp na nufin ƙazanta.
A cewar wani daga cikin mambobinta, Plaid Cymru (Jam'iyyar Wales) ba ta gamsu ba kuma ta gabatar da wasu hanyoyin.
An ce jam'iyyar Conservative Party  tana shirye  don sauya sunan, amma ta lura cewa  tsakanin MWP da Muppet (muppets), nisa ne.
A wannan yanayin, a yaren Welsh, ana furta harafin w kamar yadda ake furta harafin u a Turanci na yankin Yorkshire.
Kwamitin Majalisar, wanda ke shirin tsara dokokin da za su kawo canjin sunan, ya ce za su yanke shawara na karshe kan yadda za a nada 'yan Majalisar.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2007 (Government of Wales Act of 2017) ta bai wa majalisar dokokin Wales ikon sauya sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon wani taro na jama'a kan shawarar da aka yi na kiran Majalisar kamar majalisar kasar Wales, wanda kuma aka samu goyon baya sosai.
A kan batun sunan mambobin, Hukumar ta fi son 'yan majalisar dokokin Wales (WMP); duk da haka, yawancin mutanen Wales sun fi son MWP.
Kamar dai 'yan majalisa suna ba da wasu shawarwari, amma ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya na iya zama ainihin ciwon kai ga Elin Jones, Shugaban Majalisar, wanda ake sa ran zai gabatar da wani kudiri game da canjin sunan a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
Dokokin da suka shafi gyare-gyare za su haɗa da wasu canje-canje game da yadda majalisa ke aiki, musamman ƙa'idojin da suka shafi hana 'yan majalisa shiga majalisa da kuma tsarin tsarin kwamitin.
'Yan majalisa za su yanke shawara na ƙarshe game da sunan a lokacin da ake tattaunawa game da dokar.
