An yi wa Shugaba Erdogan maraba a birnin Cologne
A ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, shugabannin Turkiya da Jamus sun taru a Berlin don cin abincin safe a yanayi mai dadi.
Rana ce ta ƙarshe da Shugaba Erdogan ya kai ziyara a Jamus, inda ya yi ta neman inganta dangantaka tsakanin kasashen NATO.
An tattauna batutuwa da dama, kamar su 'yancin dan adam, 'yancin 'yan jarida da kuma shiga Tarayyar Turai.
Daga nan Erdogan ya tashi zuwa Cologne domin bude daya daga cikin manyan masallatai.
Ɗaya daga cikin manyan al'ummomin Turkawa da ke ƙasashen waje suna zaune a wannan birni.
'Yan sanda sun hana masu zanga-zanga 25,000 taruwa a gaban ginin, suna mai cewa saboda dalilai na tsaro, yayin da magoya bayan jam'iyyar suka samu damar zuwa kusa domin ganin shugaban kasar.
Daruruwan masu zanga-zangar adawa da Erdogan, da yawa daga Kurdawa, sun yi muryarsu, suna la'antar manufofin Erdogan da kuma shawarar gwamnatin Jamus na marabtarsa a kasarsa.
Rashin jituwa da ya taso a cikin zanga-zangar ya nuna irin ra'ayin Erdogan na biyu: wani baƙo da wasu 'yan Jamus na asalin Turkiya suka karɓe shi a matsayin jarumi, wasu kuma suka kira shi mai mulkin kama karya.
