Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa a fannin ilimin kere kere
Yayin da kasar Sin ke kara samun karfi a fannin ilimin kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa don gudanar da bincike a fannin, a cewar mai zuba jari kuma gwani a fannin ilimin kere kere Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan ya zo ne bayan da wasu jami'an gwamnatin Amurka suka yi sanarwar AI, yayin da babu wata dabarar AI a Amurka.
A daidai wannan lokaci, kasar Sin ta gabatar da taswirar tafiyarta a bara: tana shirin zama jagora a fannin kirkirar kere kere ta hanyar 2030.
 ninka kudaden bincike na AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, domin duk sauran ƙasashe suna da saurin gaba da Amurka, kuma muna neman babbar hanyar da za ta biyo baya a AI, in ji Lee.
Haɗa kuɗin zai iya ninka yiwuwar cewa babban mataki na gaba a fagen AI zai zo daga Amurka, Lee ya gaya wa CNBC a cikin wata hira da aka yi da shi a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order ya fito a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a China, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980s, a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya doke dan wasan Othello na Amurka mafi girma. Daga nan ya shiga cikin ƙungiyar gudanarwa na Microsoft Reasearch kuma ya zama shugaban Google na China.
Lee ya riga ya shiga gasar fasaha da gwamnatin Amurka ke gudanarwa, kamar gasar Robotics Challenge ta hukumar bincike kan harkokin tsaro, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a gudanar da gasar ta gaba, domin gano masu hangen nesa.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amirka suna aiki tuƙuru don su samu kuɗin da gwamnati take bukata.
 Ba China ce ke kwace shugabannin jami'o'i ba, kamfanoni ne, in ji Lee.
A 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook, Google, da wasu kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da manyan jami'ai don su yi aiki a kan AI.
Lee ya kara da cewa sauye-sauyen manufofin shige da fice na iya tallafawa kokarin Amurka kan IDA.
 Ina ganin cewa ya kamata a ba masu binciken AI katin kore ta atomatik,  in ji shi.
