Trump ya yi yakin neman zabe a West Virginia (Youtube Channel)
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron yakin neman zabensa a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Za a ƙara yin tafiya a wasu jihohi kamar Tennessee da Mississippi inda shugaban ƙasa yake da martaba.
Da aka dage zaben tabbatar da kujerar da ta ɓace a Kotun Koli, Trump yana neman samun goyon baya a zaɓen da za a yi a tsakiyar wa'adin, da kuma hana 'yan Republican rasa ikon Majalisa a zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa a kan layi?
Taron Trump a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia, zai gudana a karfe 7:00 na yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya bin sa a kan layi a ƙasa, kai tsaye a YouTube.
Trump ya kamata ya tattauna batun sauraron karar da aka yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da cin zarafin mata, wanda ya gudana a wannan makon. Za a dage zaben tabbatar da Kavanaugh a majalisar dattawa har zuwa mako guda yayin da ake gudanar da bincike na FBI.
Amma, wannan taron na musamman na taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu rinjaye a zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cikin yakin neman zabensa, shugaban Amurka ya ce, an shirya taron ne domin karfafa gwiwa da kuma tallafawa masu son shiga jam'iyyar, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da wakilai.
 Kula da majalisa wani muhimmin bangare ne na shirinsa wanda shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama a farkon wannan kamfen na zabe, in ji wani mai magana da yawun tawagar Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa, ga Reuters.
Jaridar West Virginia Metro News ta ce taron da za a yi a gidan wasan kwaikwayon na Wesbanco a birnin Wheeling, na iya jawo hankalin masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma zai iya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai a birnin Pittsburgh.
A ranar Asabar, wannan zai zama ziyarar Trump ta biyu a cikin wata guda a jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, wanda ke baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey ba cewa shugaban zai zo ya yi kokarin sake tayar da shi a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
