Kuma yanzu, shafi na mu na Almanach: "Ranar Lahadi da safe" wato ranar 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekara 136 da ta shige, an haifi Johannes Wilhelm Hans Geiger, masanin kimiyyar lissafi a Jamus.
Geiger ya ƙirƙiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna iska mai guba, kuma wannan hanyar ta sa aka ƙirƙiri na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Tun daga lokacin, ma'aunin Geiger ya zama muhimmi a al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda aka nuna a fim ɗin Bells of Coronado na shekara ta 1950, wanda ya nuna Roy Rogers da Dale Evans, wasu masana kimiyya da ba su da tabbaci:
Wani mutum ya ce: " Mene ne wannan ? "
Rogers: Wannan na'urar Geiger ne, ana amfani da ita wajen neman ma'adanai masu hasken wuta, kamar su Uranium.
Za ka iya jin tasirin da iskar rediyo take yi wa abubuwa masu ƙamshi. 
Evans: Ka faɗa mini, wannan zai yi tsalle!
