Kit Harington, tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, ya yi watsi da cutarwa na maza
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na HBO mai suna Game of Thrones.
Amma dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya yi watsi da ra'ayin jarumin, yana mai cewa irin wannan rawar a kan allo sau da yawa tana sa samari su yi kama da masu taurin kai don su sami girmamawa.
A wata hira da aka yi da jaridar Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce yana ganin akwai wani abu da ba daidai ba kuma ya yi magana game da batun guba na maza a lokacin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31 mai suna Game of Thrones, ya ce yana da niyyar magance wannan matsalar.
 Ni kaina, ina ganin mun yi wa maza ba'a. 
 Waɗanne darussa ne muka koya wa samari da suke girma, idan aka kwatanta da matsalar da muke fuskanta a yanzu? 
Kit ya ce, talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na abin da ke haifar da ƙaruwar ƙarancin maza saboda halayen da ke nuna cewa mutum namiji ne.
