Johnny English ya sake buga kwallo, Rowan Atkinson, ɗan leƙen asiri
A yau al'ada ce a bincika ma'anar Brexit a kowane sabon fim na Birtaniya kuma wannan ya yi daidai da wannan fim na wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake dawowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English, The Return.
Shin irin wannan abin dariya na nuna rashin mutuncinmu zai zama wata dama ta fitar da kayayyaki ga ƙasarmu?
Ko yaya dai, Johnny English, wanda ba shi da ƙwarewa, mai idanu masu tsalle da fuskar roba, ya sami lasisinsa na biyu a cikin wani yanayi mai rikitarwa - wannan sunan yana nuna cewa wannan babban zane ne na wasan kwaikwayo wanda aka tsara don masu sauraron fim ɗin da ba masu magana da Ingilishi ba.
Hakika, shi ne ɗan leƙen asiri wanda, duk da ƙoƙarinsa na yin sha'awa, yana da ɗan Clouseau, da ɗan ɗan ɗan Mr Bean, da kuma ɗan ɗan mutumin da ya yi ɗan ƙaramin rubutu a cikin Wasanni na Wuta a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012.
A asali, ya kuma samo asali ne daga matafiyi da kuma mutum mai ban mamaki na duniya wanda Atkinson ya taka a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard, yanzu an manta da shi, yana barin rikici a baya.
A cikin wasan kwaikwayon na ƙarshe na Johnny English, akwai lokacin farin ciki da yawa.
Na ji daɗin yadda Johnny English yake zuwa wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da yake sanye da makamai na dā, da kuma yadda ƙwanƙolin rotor ɗin suke buga kwalkwali na ɗan lokaci.
An nuna baiwar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, kodayake ba'a isa ba kuma ba'a da mahimmanci, musamman a lokacin da masu lasisi masu mahimmanci kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suna da tabbaci tare da wasan kwaikwayo.
Abin dariya ya fi mayar da hankali ga yara fiye da manya, kuma a ganina, rashin jin daɗin Johnny English ba shi da ƙira da kuma ƙwarewa fiye da wasan kwaikwayo na fim ɗin Atkinson a matsayin Bean.
Abin da ake faɗa a yau shi ne cewa ƙasar Britaniya tana da matsaloli masu tsanani.
Wani dan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin wani shafin yanar gizo na 'yan leken asiri na Birtaniya, ya bayyana sunayen duk jami'an Birtaniya da ke wurin, abin da ya ba wa jami'an tsaro mamaki - abin takaici, Kevin Eldon bai taka rawa sosai ba.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya sa aka samu matsala a matsayin firaminista wanda ke da girman kai a lokacin da ake fuskantar matsalar tattalin arziki, kuma wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga rashin amincewa da siyasa: Emma Thompson ta ba da mafi kyawun kanta tare da wannan halin da ake kira Theresa-May, amma babu wani abu da za a iya sanyawa a cikin rubutun.
Masu ba ta shawara a harkokin leken asiri sun gaya mata cewa tun da yake an yi wa kowane ɗan leken asiri da ke aiki da ita barazana, za ta bukaci ta sa wani ya yi murabus.
Wannan yana nufin cewa dole ne mu dame Johnny English da kansa, wanda yanzu yana aiki a wata babbar makaranta a matsayin malamin makaranta, amma yana koyar da darussa a asirce game da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri: wasu kyawawan farce a nan, domin English yana ba da makarantar leƙen asiri ta Rock Academy.
An dawo da English zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa na gaggawa kuma ya sami Bough, tsohon abokin aikinsa na dogon lokaci, wanda Ben Miller ya sake kafa.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, yana aiki da wani kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani rawar wasa na hockey wanda Vicki Pepperdine ya ɓata.
Saboda haka, Batman da Robin, waɗanda suka jawo matsala ga ayyukan sirri na Mai Martaba, sun koma aiki kuma sun sadu da Olga Kurylenko, kyakkyawan mace mai ban mamaki Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista ya shiga cikin haɗari ta hanyar mai karamar fasaha mai fasaha wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Birtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara wasan su na ba'a: suna kama da masu hidima, suna ƙona gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai kyau; suna haifar da rikici ta hanyar shiga cikin jirgin ruwan Volta mai tsada; kuma English ya haifar da rashin tsari na gaske lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin, tare da kwalkwali na gaskiya, don sanin cikin gidan Volta.
Dukkanin abubuwan da suka faru a wannan fim ɗin sun tabbata, amma duk da haka, akwai abubuwa da yawa da za su iya shafan yaran.
Wannan fim ne mai kyau.
Na yi tunani, kamar sauran fina-finan Johnny English: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da za ta iya nuna kwarewarta ba?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa ta tsara wani shiri da zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki na kwana hudu amma a biya su na kwana biyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn dole ne ta duba wani tsari na musamman wanda zai ba wa 'yan Birtaniya damar yin aiki kwana hudu a mako - amma a biya su biyar.
Kamar dai jam'iyyar tana son shugabannin kasuwanci su ba ma'aikata ƙarin ranar hutu don su amfana daga tanadin da aka yi ta hanyar fasaha ta wucin gadi.
Wannan zai ba ma'aikata damar samun hutun mako na kwana uku, kuma su ci gaba da samun albashi iri ɗaya.
Wasu majiyoyi sun ce wannan ra'ayin ya yi daidai da shirin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin da ta yi na mayar da kasar ga ma'aikata.
An amince da sauya zuwa mako guda na kwana huɗu a taron ma'aikata a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su amfana daga canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'i a jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa Sunday Times cewa:  Ana sa ran za a sanar da wani bita kan manufofin kafin karshen shekara. 
 Ba za a yi wannan ba cikin dare ɗaya, amma aikin kwana huɗu na aiki manufa ce da ta zo daidai da tsarin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata da kuma dabarun masana'antu gaba ɗaya .
Jam'iyyar Labour ba za ta kasance ta farko da ta goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, tun da Jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwana hudu a lokacin yakin neman zaben 2017.
Amma a yanzu haka, ba a goyon bayan wannan burin a jam'iyyar Labour baki ɗaya.
