Mr. McDonnell ya ce yana da niyyar dawo da mulki daga hannun masu gudanarwa da kuma masu cin riba a kamfanonin amfanin jama'a.
Shirye-shiryen maye gurbin shugaban kasar kuma sun nuna cewa masu hannun jarin kamfanonin ruwa na iya rashin samun kudaden shiga gaba daya saboda gwamnatin Labour na iya yin  deductions  saboda zargin rashin bin doka.
Ya kuma tabbatar da shirinsa na shigar da ma'aikata cikin kwamitin gudanarwa na kamfanoni da kuma kafa wani asusun masu hannun jari wanda zai biya kashi 10 cikin 100 na babban birnin kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikata, wanda zai tara ribar har zuwa £500 a shekara.
