Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na shekara-shekara na kiɗa da ke da taurari masu yawa da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa: kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda yanzu ya kai shekara ta bakwai, zai ga dubun dubatan mutane suna zuwa babban filin shakatawa na Central Park don ba kawai su ji dadin ayyukan masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma su wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar bikin, wato kawo karshen matsanancin talauci nan da shekarar 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara gudanar da shi a shekarar 2012, wani bangare ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke neman kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta (sai dai idan kun kasance a shirye ku biya tikitin VIP), masu kallo dole ne su yi wasu ayyuka, ko ayyuka, kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel ga wani shugaban duniya, yin waya, ko kuma yin wani abu mai amfani don wayar da kan jama'a game da yaki da talauci.
Amma yaya Global Citizen zai iya cimma burinsa a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ta hanyar yin wasan kwaikwayo na kyauta yana shawo kan mutane su nemi a yi musu kira, ko kuwa wani misali ne na yin clicktivism - inda mutane suke tunanin cewa za su iya kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu a takarda ko aika tweet?
Tun daga shekarar 2011, Global Citizen ta samu fiye da miliyan 19 na tallafi daga magoya bayanta, wadanda ke neman a cimma manufofi daban-daban.
A cewar kungiyar, wadannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen karfafawa shugabannin duniya gwiwa da kuma aiwatar da manufofi masu darajar sama da dala biliyan 37 da ake sa ran za su sauya rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta yi ambaton alkawura 390 da kuma sanarwar da ta yi dangane da ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka biya ko kuma aka cire.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa, kuɗin da aka yi tanadinsa ya yi tasiri kai tsaye a kan mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
A cikin manyan alkawuran akwai The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta Burtaniya da ke hada kai da masu zuba jari da masu gudanar da ayyukan da suka yi alkawarin taimaka wa yara su samu cikakkiyar damar da suke da ita, yayin da suka yi alkawarin bai wa Rwanda fam miliyan 35 domin kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan sun samu sakonni sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
 Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da tallafi, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihin , in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan shirin The Power of Nutrition, a wani biki da aka gudanar a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an fara ayyuka sama da 5,000 na neman Birtaniya ta inganta ciyar da uwaye da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da bayar da tallafi ga wani shiri mai suna The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai amfana mata da yara miliyan 5 a cikin tsarin ciyarwa.
A amsa ga ɗaya daga cikin tambayoyin da aka fi yi a shafinsa, me ya sa kake ganin za a iya kawar da talauci?
Global Citizen ta ce:  Hanyar zuwa can za ta yi tsawo da wuya, wani lokacin za mu fadi kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin kare hakkin jama'a da na 'yanci da suka riga sun wuce, za mu yi nasara, domin tare muna da ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe suna cikin masu yin wasan da za su yi a birnin New York a wannan shekara, inda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su yi wa wasan kwaikwayon.
Amurka na iya amfani da Sojojin Ruwa don kafa wani shinge don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida
Don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwanni, ciki har da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, Washington na iya yin amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa na Amurka idan ya cancanta, in ji Ryan Zinke, sakataren harkokin cikin gida na Amurka, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya ce kasancewar Rasha a Syria - musamman inda take aiki bisa bukatar gwamnatin da ta dace - wata hujja ce da ke ba ta damar gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin suna Gabas ta Tsakiya ne domin su yi ciniki a kan makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, kudancin tsakiyar Turai", in ji shi.
A cewar wakilin gwamnati, akwai hanyoyin magance wannan matsalar.
 Amurka za ta iya, tare da rundunar sojin ruwanmu, ta tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna buɗe kuma idan ya zama dole, ta yi toshe don tabbatar da cewa ba a sayar da makamashin ta ba , ya kara da cewa.
Zinke yana magana ne ga masu halartar taron da Ƙungiyar Amfani da Makamashi ta Amfani da Ita, wata ƙungiya mai zaman kanta wadda take kiran kanta 'yar magana da yawun masu amfani da makamashi a Amirka.
Ya kwatanta hanyoyin da Washington ke bi wajen hulda da Rasha da Iran, inda ya ce a gaskiya suna kama da juna.
 Game da Iran da Rasha, zaɓin tattalin arziki ya fi ko ƙasa da haka ne a cikin amfanin gona da maye gurbin man fetur , ya ce, yayin da yake magana game da Rasha yana cewa tana da  fiye da igiya ɗaya a cikin baka  tare da tattalin arziƙin da ya dogara da man fetur.
Wannan ya zo ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ta yi alkawarin kara fitar da iskar gas dinta zuwa Turai, inda za ta maye gurbin Rasha, wadda ta fi masu amfani da ita a Turai rahusa.
Don yin haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta fice daga aikin samar da bututun mai mai suna Nord Stream 2, wanda Trump ya ce ya sa birnin Berlin ya zama fursuna na Moscow.
A lokatai da dama, Moscow ta jaddada cewa aikin Nord Stream 2, mai darajar dala biliyan 11, wanda ake sa ran zai ninka karfin da ake da shi a yanzu zuwa miliyan biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ta ce, tsananin adawa da Washington ke yi da wannan shiri, ya samo asali ne daga dalilai na tattalin arziki, kuma misali ne na rashin gaskiya.
A jawabin da ya yi a watan Satumba a Moscow bayan ganawa da Rick Perry, Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka, Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Alexander Novak ya ce, "Ina ganin mun yarda cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama kayan aiki na matsa lamba ba kuma masu amfani su zabi masu samar da su".
Matsayin Amurka ya jawo hankulan Jamus, wadda ta sake tabbatar da hannu cikin wannan shiri.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI) ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta guje wa shiga cikin manufofin makamashi na Turai da kuma yarjejeniyar da aka kulla tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta kasa ta tsoma baki a samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, daraktan kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
