Wani bincike da Cibiyar Bincike a Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk da kuma jaridar Boston Globe suka yi ya nuna cewa kashi 58 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata ta tsaya takara ba.
