Sarah Palin ta yi magana game da PTSD na Track Palin a lokacin taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya yi shekara guda a Iraki bayan da aka tura shi aiki a watan Satumba.
A ranar Litinin da daddare, an kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da aikata wani laifi na cin zarafin cikin gida.
 Abin da ɗana yake ji a yanzu, abin da yake ji a lokacin da ya dawo gida, zan iya danganta shi da sauran iyalai da ke fama da sakamakon PTSD da kuma wasu raunuka da sojoji ke dawowa da su  ta gaya wa jama'a a taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira kama ta da "batun da ba a yarda da shi ba" kuma ta ce game da ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji "sun dawo ne da bambanci, sun yi taurin kai, suna tambayar kansu ko za a girmama abin da takwarorinsu da mambobin rundunar sojin sama, da kuma kowane soja, suka ba wa ƙasar".
Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun rundunar 'yan sanda ta Wasilla, ya ce an kama shi a Wasilla, Alaska, a ranar Litinin, kuma an tuhume shi da cin zarafin mata da kuma cin zarafinta a cikin gida, wanda ya shafi rahoton cin zarafin mata da kuma mallakar makami a cikin maye.
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan kalubalantar sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia suna goyon bayan a shigar da kara a kotu kan sabuwar manufar Amurka da ta hana bautar da wadanda suka gudu daga 'yan bindiga ko kuma ta'addanci na cikin gida.
A ranar Juma'a a Washington, wakilai daga jihohi 18 da gundumar sun shigar da takarda a madadin wani mai neman mafaka wanda ya yi adawa da wannan manufar, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai ƙarar ba a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da Ƙungiyar 'Yancin Bil'adama ta Amirka ta yi a watan Agusta game da dokar tarayya.
Ta ce abokin aikinta  da 'ya'yanta maza, mambobin 'yan bindiga masu ta'addanci , sun yi mata fyade, amma hukumomin Amurka sun yanke shawarar ƙin neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas.
Masu gabatar da kara na jihar da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, da ke da yawan neman mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin kasashen da ke fama da matsalar 'yan bindiga da kuma cin zarafin mata.
Sabuwar manufar Amurka ta neman mafaka ta soke hukuncin da Hukumar Kula da Kula da Shige da Fice ta yanke a shekarar 2014 wanda ya bai wa baƙi da ke gudun tashin hankali a gida damar neman mafaka.
Karl Racine, babban lauyan gundumar Columbia, ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar  ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa .
 Dokar tarayya ta ce dole ne a bincika duk wani neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da kuma yanayin da ake nema, kuma irin wannan haramcin ya sabawa wannan ka'ida , in ji Amicus Curiae a cikin takardar sa.
Lauyoyi sun kuma yi jayayya a cikin takardar cewa, dokar hana baƙi shiga tana cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna mai cewa, suna da damar zama 'yan kasuwa da kuma samar da aikin da ake bukata.
A watan Yuni ne babban lauyan ƙasar Jeff Sessions ya umurci alƙalan 'yan gudun hijira da su daina ba wa waɗanda suka tsere wa cin zarafin mata da miji da kuma 'yan bindiga mafaka.
 An ba da mafaka ga mutanen da suka bar ƙasarsu na asali saboda tsanantawa ko tsoro saboda launin fata, imani, ƙasa, kasancewa cikin wani rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayin siyasa,  Sessions ya ce a cikin sanarwar da ya yi game da wannan manufar a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
 Ba a taɓa tsara mafaka don rage yawan matsalolin da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a dukan duniya ba, ko da kuwa mafi tsanani. 
An yi gagarumar yunkurin ceto a Palu yayin da adadin wadanda suka mutu ya ninka a cikin gagarumar neman wadanda suka tsira
Yanayin waɗanda suka tsira ya daɗa muni.
"Ina jin takaici sosai", in ji Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiyar 'ya'ya mai shekara 35, yayin da take ta'azantar da ɗanta da ke da zazzaɓi a Palu, wani wurin kwashe mutane daga garin da babu kowa.
 Ana kawo gawawwakin mutane a kowane lokaci.
Ba a samun ruwa mai tsabta.
An ga mazauna garin suna shiga gidajensu da suka lalace, suna tattara kayayyakin da suka yi ruwa da su, suna ƙoƙarin ceton duk wani abin da suka samu.
An yi wa daruruwan mutane rauni kuma an rufe asibitoci da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta lalata.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, ciki har da Dwi Haris, wanda ke fama da karyewar kashin baya da kafadu, sun huta a gaban asibitin soji na Palu, inda ake kula da marasa lafiya a waje saboda ci gaba da tashin hankali.
Ya yi kuka sa'ad da ya ba da labarin yadda ya ji girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da ta girgiza ɗakin otal na bene na biyar inda yake zama da matarsa da 'yarsa.
Ba mu sami lokacin da za mu tsere ba.
"An murkushe ni a cikin bangon, ina tsammanin", in ji Haris ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press, inda ya ce danginsa suna cikin gari domin bikin aure.
Na ji matata tana kuka don taimako, amma sai na yi shiru.
Ban san abin da ya faru da ita ko kuma ɗana ba.
Ina fatan sun kasance lafiya.
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin barazanar ta hanyar tallar yaɗa labarai
Makon daya bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wani talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke yabon amfanin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba da ta gabata, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da karin kudin da China Daily ta biya a Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa  bayan ya zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Da yake zargin Beijing da son shiga cikin zaben Amurka, Trump ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka gaya wa Reuters cewa sabon mataki ne a cikin wani yunkuri da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan China.
Yayin da ya zama ruwan dare ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace domin su inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a yanzu haka suna cikin yakin cinikayya da ya kai su ga saka haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
A farkon yakin cinikayya, matakan harajin da China ta dauka na nufin a gurgunta masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohi kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na China da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, in ji Branstad a wani labari da ya fito a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, tana ninka barazanar ta ta hanyar wallafa farfaganda a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci.
 A wajen yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China ta yi amfani da al'adar Amurka na 'yancin magana da 'yancin jarida ta hanyar saka tallace-tallace da ake biya a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register , in ji Branstad.
 A bangaren 'yan jarida a Beijing, ba za ka ga muryoyin masu zanga-zanga ba, kuma ba za ka ga ainihin ra'ayoyin da suka bambanta da mutanen China ke da shi ba game da yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna bin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin sosai, ya rubuta. 
Ya kara da cewa, wata babbar jarida a kasar Sin ta kauce wa buga labarin, ba tare da ta bayyana ko wane ne ba.
Masu sharhi sun ce 'yan Republican na janye hankalin masu jefa kuri'a yayin da ake gab da zaben tsakiyar shekara saboda matsalar Kavanaugh.
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican da dama ke goyon bayan Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a kotun koli a cikin wani yanayi na zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a iya samun mummunar amsa, musamman ma tsakanin mata, a lokacin zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
Tunanin da ke kewaye da wannan al'amari ya kasance mai cike da damuwa, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna a fili cewa suna son a yi zabe.
A cikin wata kasida da aka buga a The Hill a ranar 29 ga Satumba, Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse ya ce ba za a iya komawa baya ba.
Reeher ya kara da cewa yana shakkar cewa kokarin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Ariz.) ya yi na minti na karshe na neman a gudanar da bincike na FBI zai isa ya kwantar da fushin masu jefa kuri'a.
Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma kakakin kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, ta ce, "mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi ba gobe, ba a watan Nuwamba ba", in ji ta a ranar 28 ga watan Satumba, a cewar jaridar Washington.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, in ji Mic, masu zanga-zanga sun rera waka mai suna "November Is Coming" a zauren majalisar dattawa yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zabi su ci gaba da nada Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford.
 Ƙoƙarin da ake yi na dimokiradiyya da kuma motsawa zai yi yawa, in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa da ba ya son bangare.
Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya yi yawa, gaskiya ne.
Amma za a iya samun ƙaruwa, musamman a tsakanin mata masu jefa ƙuri'a a ƙauyuka da kuma matasa masu zaɓe masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29 waɗanda, ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa, sau da yawa ba sa jefa ƙuri'a. 
Tun kafin Ford ya bayyana a fili cewa an yi wa wanda ya zaɓa a kotun koli fyade, manazarta sun ce za a yi tawaye idan 'yan Republican suka amince da shi.
A cewar NBC News, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa, Michael Steele, ya ce a farkon makon da ya gabata cewa, "Wannan ya zama rikici ga jam'iyyar Republican".
 Ba wai kawai batun kwamitin zabe ko na karshe ba, ko kuma nadin Kavanaugh, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka gudanar da lamarin da kuma yadda suka magance shi , in ji Guy Cecil, darektan US Priorities, wani rukuni da ke taimakawa 'yan Democrat da aka zaɓa, a jaridar talabijin.
Amma, bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, jama'ar Amirka sun rarrabu a kan abin da ya kamata a gaskata game da jam'iyyun biyu, da ƙarancin rinjaye da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyun biyu.
Wani sabon bincike na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na mutanen da aka yi wa tambayoyi sun gaskata da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun gaskata da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin wataƙila ko kuma Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka ce haka game da Ford.
Jaridar The Guardian ta ce, FBI na binciken zargin da Ford da kuma Deborah Ramirez suka yi, bayan da Sanata Flake ya matsa musu.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade yayin da yake cikin maye a lokacin da yake da shekara 17.
Ramirez ya yi ikirarin cewa lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980, dan takarar kotun koli ya nuna masa al'aurarsa a lokacin wani biki.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kaddamar da sabuwar intanet domin kalubalantar Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa sabuwar kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da aka yi wa wannan ƙwararren masanin fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke amfani da dandalin Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda aka ba izini su shiga wannan ko wannan bayanin.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da aka ba Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wasa da cewa Inrupt yana da niyyar mamaye duniya.
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da kaddamar da shirin.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi ko DPL.
Wannan na iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalanda, laburaren waƙa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna nan a lokaci guda a cikin burauzar yanar gizo guda.
Abin da ke musamman game da shagon adana bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani ne ke da cikakken ikon yanke shawara game da wanda zai iya samun dama ga wane irin bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan  alhakin mutum ta hanyar bayanai .
A cewar Shugaba John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, aiyuka da kuma basira da suka dace domin kowa ya samu amfani da Solid.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandalin tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu 'yan kwangilar masu ci gaba da ke aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'ummar masu aikin sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere-kere a duk faɗin duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke kan shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da  Facebook da Google  ba game da ko za su yi canji na gaba daya inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su ya lalace gaba daya a lokaci guda.
 Ba ma neman izinin su. 
A wata kasida a Medium ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa, manufar dInrupt ita ce samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da nufin kare mutunci da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka gina a kan Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee a Massachusetts Institute of Technology ya canja hanyar sadarwa ta hanyar kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na hanyar sadarwa.
Duk da cewa ya fara Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Open.
 Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo , in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: An Ba da Kyautar Victoria ga Wani Limamin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
An yi bikin bikin bikin mutuwar limamin Cocin Ingila guda ɗaya da aka ba lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya a garin da ya fito shekaru 100 bayan haka.
Lt. Col. Bernard Vann ya sami wannan girmamawa a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, yayin harin da aka kai a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, wani ɗan bindiga ya kashe shi bayan kwana huɗu, kuma bai san cewa ya sami babban gata a ƙasar Britaniya ba.
Yaransa biyu sun buɗe wani dutse na tunawa da shi a wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire, a ranar Asabar da ta gabata.
Michael Vann, ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, ya ce yana da ban mamaki sosai a nuna dutsen daidai shekara 100 bayan nasarar kakansa.
Jaridar London Gazette ta ce a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Laftanar Janar Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa a St. Quentin Canal a cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai ƙarfi daga bindigogi da bindigogi.
Daga baya ya ruga zuwa layin wuta, kuma da ƙarfin zuciya ya jagoranci layin kafin ya harba bindiga guda ɗaya da kansa kuma ya kashe sojoji uku.
A ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wani ɗan Jamus mai harbi ya kashe Laftanar Janar Vann, fiye da wata ɗaya kafin yaƙin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da kakansa ya yi  abu ne da ba zan taɓa iya kaiwa ba, amma abin da ya sa ni tawali'u .
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann, sun kuma saka kambi bayan bikin da ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ta gudanar.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin yabawa sosai kasancewarsa wani ɓangare na bikin  kuma ya kara da cewa  ƙarfin hali na ainihin gwarzo yana nunawa a cikin goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su ba shi .
Masu sha'awar wasan kwaikwayo na Mixed Martial Arts sun kasance a farke duk dare don kallon Bellator 206.
Ka yi tunanin wannan, ka yi dare kana kallon Bellator 206 mai cike da kaya, amma ba ka ga ainihin abin da ya faru ba.
A San José, an yi gwagwarmaya guda 13, daga cikinsu shida a kan babban faifai, kuma an watsa su kai tsaye a duk dare a Channel 5 a Burtaniya.
Da karfe shida na safe, lokacin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald ke shirin yin kara, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamaki lokacin da aka canza watsa shirye-shiryen zuwa Peppa Pig.
Wasu sun yi fushi da kasancewa a faɗake har ƙarfe ɗaya na safe musamman don yaƙi.
Wani mai goyon baya a shafin Twitter ya bayyana sauyawar zuwa zane mai ban dariya na yara a matsayin  wani irin mummunan wasa  .
Game da watsa shirye-shiryen, babban mataimakin shugaban kasuwanci da sadarwa na Bellator, Dave Schwartz, ya ce  dokar gwamnati ta ce  a karfe 6 na safe, wannan abun bai dace ba, don haka sai suka koma shirye-shiryen yara .
"Peppa the pig", na yi.
Scott Coker, shugaban kamfanin Bellator, ya ce za su ci gaba da shirin su domin su hada da masu kallon gidan talabijin na Birtaniya a nan gaba.
"Ina ganin idan na yi tunani game da sake watsa shirye-shiryen, ina ganin za mu iya samun mafita", in ji Coker.
 Amma, sa'a shida na safe ce a ranar Lahadi, kuma ba za mu iya samun mafita ba sai ranar Lahadi, wato Litinin, lokacinmu.
Amma muna aiki a kan hakan.
Ku yi imani da ni, lokacin da shirin ya sauya, akwai saƙonni da yawa a hanyoyi biyu kuma ba duka abokantaka ba ne.
Mun yi ƙoƙari mu gyara shi, mun yi tunanin cewa matsalar fasaha ce.
Amma wannan ba matsala ba ce, batun gwamnati ne.
Ina tabbatar muku cewa ba za a sake yin hakan ba.
Za mu yi wasa biyar maimakon shida kamar yadda muka saba yi, kuma mun yi kokarin karawa magoya baya baya, kuma mun bata komai.
Wannan yanayi ne mai ban tausayi.
Tom Daley ya ji cewa shi kasa ne a batun jima'i
Mai tsere-tsere na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin cewa ba shi da daraja a gaban mutane saboda jima'i - amma hakan ya sa ya yi nasara.
Matashin mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci ba har zuwa lokacin da ya shiga makarantar sakandare cewa ba kowa ba ne kamar ni.
A cikin shirin farko na Radio 4 Desert Island Discs wanda Lauren Laverne ta gabatar, ya ce ya yi magana game da batun 'yancin luwadi don ba wa wasu bege.
Ya kuma ce zama mahaifi ya sa ya daina sha'awar yin nasara a wasannin Olympics.
Mai gabatar da shirin Kirsty Young ta dauki hutun watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
Ya bayyana a matsayin wanda aka yiwa rauni a farkon wasan Laverne, Daley ya bayyana cewa ya ji  ƙasa da  duk sauran yara suna girma saboda  ba a yarda da shi ba don son yara maza da mata .
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, wannan jin kasa da bambanci ne ya ba ni iko da ƙarfin da nake bukata don yin nasara".
Don kada ya sa kowa ya yi sanyin gwiwa lokacin da suka koyi gaskiya game da jima'i, ya so ya tabbatar da cewa shi wani abu ne, ya ci gaba.
Gwarzon dan wasan Olympics mai lashe lambar tagulla yanzu sanannen dan gay ne kuma ya yi amfani da halartarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Australia don neman karin kasashe su haramta luwadi.
Ya ce yana magana ne saboda yana jin ya yi sa'a da ya iya rayuwa a fili ba tare da wani tasiri ba kuma yana so ya ba da bege ga wasu.
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce bai yi tsammanin zai so wani mutum ba - dan fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013
Daley ta auri wanda ya lashe kyautar Oscar a shekarar da ta gabata, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
 Lokacin da mutum ya ga abubuwa da yawa a irin wannan ƙuruciya  - ya shiga gasar Olympics ta farko yana ɗan shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - ya furta cewa yana da wuya a sami mutum a shekarunsa wanda ya sami irin abubuwan da suka faru.
