Bayan da aka ji rauni a kan kai, Christion Abercrombie ya yi aikin tiyata na gaggawa
Sselon Mike Organ na Tennessee State, Christion Abercrombie, dan wasan Tigers na Tennessee, ya yi aikin gaggawa bayan ya ji rauni a kan kai a ranar Asabar a lokacin da Vanderbilt Commodores suka ci 31-27.
