Abercrombie, ɗan wasa ne a shekara ta biyu, yana kakar sa ta farko a jihar Tennessee bayan da aka tura shi daga Illinois.
Ya ci kwallaye biyar a ranar Asabar kafin ya fita daga wasan, wanda ya kai jimlarsa na kakar zuwa 18.
