Masu sayen ƙasashen waje za su biya ƙarin kuɗin hatimi idan sun sayi gida a Burtaniya kuma za a yi amfani da ƙarin kuɗin don taimaka wa marasa gida a ƙarƙashin sabbin tsare-tsaren Conservative
