Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ya afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda hukumomi suka sanar, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai karu.
Tun da yake ba a iya samun bayanai daga tashar jiragen ruwa ba, ma'aikatan agaji ba su samu wani bayani ba daga yankin Donggala, wanda ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga cikin gidajensu sakamakon bala'in.
Wasu muhimman abubuwa game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne, wanda ke kan iyakar wani kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda aka kiyasta yawansa ya kai 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
An kiyasta yawan mutanen yankin, yanki na yanki wanda ke ƙasa da lardi, ya kai mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan bangarorin tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman ma yankin Donggala na gabar teku.
Ma'adinan nickel ma babban aiki ne a lardin, amma galibi yana cikin Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayin Bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce, Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da girgizar kasa sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afka yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Ƙasar Indonisiya tana kan Tekun Fasifik kuma tana yawan girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu aukuwa na girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a ranar 26 ga Disamba a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na ƙasar Indonesia ta jawo tsunami da ya mamaye ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gaɓar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin mutanen a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta girgiza gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane ɗari da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gaɓar teku na Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afka kudu maso gabashin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya afka gaɓar tekun kudu kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 ta girgiza birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta halaka tsibirin Mentawai da ke gaɓar teku na Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa ta girgiza yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba, wanda ya tunatar da mazauna yankin da raunin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka yi a shekarar 2004.
Ba a yi wata annobar tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta girgiza tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasar ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta hana dubban masu yawon buɗe ido shiga cikin birnin.
