Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargin shi ne wanda ya kai hari a birnin New York, wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a yi ba a jihar saboda wani laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
An ce Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da babbar mota da ya yi hayar daga Home Depot don kai hari kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da kafa da kuma mai hawan keke a watan Oktoba da ya gabata.
Don a yanke masa hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci a tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya yi kisan kai da gangan ga wadanda aka kashe da kuma raunana su da gangan, a cewar sanarwar da aka shigar a gaban kotun da ke kula da shari'ar da ke yankin kudancin birnin New York.
An rubuta cewa za a iya yanke masa hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu.
Makonni bayan wannan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta yanke wa Saipov hukuncin kisa kan laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai don karbar kudi, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a shari'ar aikata laifuka da aka tsara, da kuma laifuka guda daya na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci  shiri sosai , kuma an yi tunaninsa , suna mai cewa hanyar da Saipov ya yi amfani da ita  abin ƙyama ne, mai zalunci da lalata .
 Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lalacewa da kuma asarar rayuka , in ji sanarwar niyya.
Biyar cikin waɗanda suka mutu 'yan yawon buɗe ido ne daga ƙasar Ajantina.
