A shekarar 1953 ne aka yi hukuncin kisa a shari'ar da aka yi a New York, a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe don yin makirci da kuma leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a cikin shekaru biyu bayan yakin sanyi.
