Dundee Stars sun share asarar da suka sha a ranar Juma'a a gasar Elite League da Belfast Giants, inda suka ci wasan da suka yi a Dundee, 5-3 a ranar Asabar.
'Yan wasan Giants sun buɗe ƙwallo da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka ci biyu.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun kawo wasan a gida kafin Dwyer ya mayar da Giants da fifiko.
François Bouchard ya daidaita wa Dundee kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci kwallaye biyu, ya tabbatar da nasarar.
Wannan ne karo na uku da 'yan wasan Adam Keefe suka rasa a gasar Elite League, bayan sun ci Dundee da ci 2-1 a ranar Juma'a da daddare a Belfast.
Wannan shi ne karo na huɗu da 'yan wasan biyu suka yi karo da juna a kakar, kuma Giants sun ci nasara a wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya ba da fifiko a minti na huɗu, 3:35, ta hanyar Kendall McFaull, yayin da David Rutherford ya yi amfani da Beauvillier wanda ya ninka fare minti huɗu daga baya.
A lokacin da aka fara aiki sosai, Sullivan ya sake dawo da 'yan wasan gida a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya koma sabis na Cownie a 15:16, tare da daidaitawa.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da Giants sun ci gaba kafin hutun farko lokacin da ya buga kwallo na biyu na maraice a ƙarshen farkon.
Ƙungiyar gida ta sake haɗuwa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa da ci da ya ba da damar ci gaba da ƙidaya a 27:37.
