Yadda Yakin Ciniki Tsakanin Amurka Da China Zai Iya Amfanar Beijing
An ji muryar mutane da yawa a farkon yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, kuma ko da yake ba a gama yaƙin ba, masana sun ce rashin jituwa tsakanin ƙasashen zai iya amfanar Beijing a dogon lokaci.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi gargadin farko a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi girma ya zo ne a wannan makon tare da sabon haraji kan kayayyakin da suka kai dala biliyan 200 (Ft biliyan 150), wanda ya sanya haraji kan rabin kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
A duk lokacin da aka yi wannan, Beijing ta mayar da martani, kwanan nan ta saka haraji na kashi 5 zuwa 10 bisa dari a kan kayayyakin Amurka biliyan 60.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta yi daidai da Amurka, kuma ba zai yiwu ba tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ya yi sanyi nan da nan.
Yin watsi da Washington na nufin yin biyayya ga bukatun, amma yin biyayya a fili a gaban Amurka zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Masana sun ce idan har Beijing ta yi nasara, matsin lamba na yakin cinikayya na Amurka na iya yin tasiri mai kyau a kan China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro tsakanin tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani mataki na siyasa da aka ɗauka da sauri a Washington ko kuma a Beijing zai iya kafa yanayi mai kyau don raguwar tattalin arziki a kowanne daga cikin ƙasashen ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu lura da al'amura suka sani", Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike da ke mai da hankali kan Asiya, ta gaya wa wani rukunin tunani na Cibiyar Sabon Tsaron Amurka.
An Shirya Kasar Siriya Don Dawowar 'Yan Gudun Hijira, Inji Ministan Harkokin Waje
Kasar Siriya ta bayyana aniyarta ta amince da komawar 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai, kuma ta nemi taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta sha wahala sakamakon yakin da ta shafe sama da shekaru bakwai.
A lokacin da yake jawabi ga babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al-Moualem ya ce halin da ake ciki a kasar na inganta.
 A yau, yanayin da ake ciki ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci , in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da al'amuran al'ada.
Dukkan yanayi sun kasance a yanzu don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira da son rai zuwa ƙasar da aka tilasta musu su bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na gefe guda da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya ta ce mutane fiye da miliyan biyar da dubu ɗari biyar ne suka gudu daga ƙasar Siriya tun lokacin da aka soma yaƙin a shekara ta 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suke zaune a ƙasar suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi farin ciki da samun taimakon sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Ya ce ba zai amince da taimakon da aka ba shi ba, ko kuma na kasashen da ke tallafa wa 'yan tawayen.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta doke tawagar Amurka da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Golf National kusa da Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu, Amirka ta yi hasara sau shida a Turai kuma ba ta ci gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin ne lokacin da tawagar Thomas Bjorn ta wuce maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin doke Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a gasar, ya jefa kwallo a cikin ruwa a rami na 16 a wasan, inda ya ci Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya yi fice a duk wasannin da ya buga, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka taba samun ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya yi nasara da ci 5-4 a kan dan wasan da ya fi kasa a Turai Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, wanda shi ne mafi kyawun dan wasan golf a duniya, ya yi nasara da ci 2 da 1 a kan dan wasan Ingila Ian Poulter, wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe.
Tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup takwas, Sergio Garcia na Spain ya zama zakaran Turai na kowane lokaci tare da jimillar maki 25.5 na aikinsa.
A yawancin lokaci, ba na kuka, amma a yau, ina kuka sosai.
Wannan shekara ce mai cike da matsaloli.
Ina godiya ga Thomas don ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki sosai, ina farin ciki cewa zan sami ƙoƙon.
Abin da ya fi muhimmanci shi ne ƙungiyar, kuma ina farin cikin cewa na taimaka mata, in ji Garcia cikin farin ciki bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya ba da ita ga dan kasarsa John Ram wanda ya doke Tiger Woods da ci 2-1 a wasan daya-daya a ranar Lahadi da ta gabata.
