Woods ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu da ya yi a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki ga ɗaya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan golf na dukan lokaci, wanda ya lashe gasar golf guda 14 a duniya, bayan Jack Nicklaus.
Ƙungiyar 'yan wasan Amurka ta yi fama da samun hanyar zuwa gasar a duk karshen mako, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasan golf a matakin farko a duk lokacin gasar.
