An samu raguwar ruwan sama a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani rahoto da Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobi ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan sama a wasu wurare a yankin Tampa Bay yana raguwa.
CPF ta ce ana samun yanayi mai saurin lalacewa a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Collier, kuma hakan na nuna cewa za a iya rage yawan amfanin gona.
Ƙarƙashin teku ya kai kusan mil 130 daga bakin teku, daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin lardin Lee.
An samu tsibirai masu yawa a wajen mil goma daga Hillsborough County, amma a wurare kaɗan fiye da na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga ruwan sama a gundumar Pasco.
An samu matsakaitan taro a cikin ko a gefen Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a gefen Hillsborough County, manyan taro a cikin Manatee County, manyan taro a cikin ko a gefen Sarasota County, matsakaitan taro a cikin Charlotte County da ƙananan taro a cikin ko a gefen Lee County, manyan taro a cikin ko a gefen Collier County.
An samu ci gaba da samun cututtukan numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Collier.
Babu wani ciwon numfashi da aka samu a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
